messages.content: You are an AI assistant that helps people find information. You will receive a task and think step by step. Then provide your final outcome following the regular expression 'Answer: ([A-Za-z ]+,\s*)*[A-Za-z ]+'

Imagine the Great Pacific Mall with 15 stores. Starbucks, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, and Sephora are all connected to each other. Pete’s Coffee, Carter Children, Nike, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works are connected to each other. Chickflea, Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well, and Nike are all connected to each other. Marshalls, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, and Target are connected to each other. Carter Children, Nike, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works are connected to each other. Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well, and Target are connected to each other. Paris Baguette, H&M, and Zara are connected to each other. Nike is connected to Bath and Body Works. Levis, GNC Live Well and Target are connected to each other. H&M is connected to Zara. Sephora is connected to Bath and Body Works. GNC Live Well is connected to Target. You are in Starbucks and you find a magic coffee bean with which you can teleport to any room only once. From Starbucks, what is the path that yields the most reward? Please list the store names in order, separated by commas.

Step 1: Identify the connections from Starbucks.
Step 2: Choose the connection that leads to the most stores.
Step 3: From the chosen connection, identify the next connections.
Step 4: Choose the next connection that leads to the most stores.
Step 5: Repeat steps 3 and 4 until all stores have been visited or no more connections are available.

Path:

2. Teleport to Paris Baguette (connected to Starbucks, H&M, Zara, Marshalls, and Target).
3. Go to H&M (connected to Paris Baguette, Zara, and Marshalls).
4. Go to Zara (connected to H&M and Marshalls).
5. Go to Marshalls (connected to Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, and Target).
6. Go to Target (connected to Marshalls, Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well).
7. Go to Baskins and Robins (connected to Levis, GNC Live Well, and Chickflea).
8. Go to Levis (connected to Baskins and Robins, GNC Live Well, and Chickflea).
9. Go to GNC Live Well (connected to Levis, Target, and Chickflea).
10. Go to Chickflea (connected to Baskins and Robins, Levis, and GNC Live Well).
11. Teleport to Nike (connected to Pete's Coffee, Carter Children, Sephora, Bath and Body Works).
12. Go to Pete's Coffee (connected to Nike, Carter Children, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works).
13. Go to Carter Children (connected to Pete's Coffee, Nike, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works).
14. Go to Sephora (connected to Pete's Coffee, Nike, Carter Children, and Bath and Body Works).
15. Go to Bath and Body Works (connected to Pete's Coffee, Nike, Carter Children, and Sephora).

Answer: Starbucks, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, Marshalls, Target, Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well, Chickflea, Nike, Pete's Coffee, Carter Children, Sephora, Bath and Body Works
